106
00:08:26,300 --> 00:08:28,500
Is it ambition?

107
00:08:28,700 --> 00:08:30,400
Yeah.

108
00:08:30,700 --> 00:08:33,100
You're no mystery
to me, boy.

109
00:08:33,300 --> 00:08:36,800
