00:10:01,800 --> 00:10:04,700
Gets a little rough
in there sometimes.

125
00:10:04,900 --> 00:10:07,600
Well, what happened
to it?

126
00:10:07,800 --> 00:10:09,500
Duct tape.

127
00:10:09,700 --> 00:10:13,100
Oh.

128
00:10:13,700 --> 00:10:17,700
