to hold on to somebody for a minute.

144
00:11:22,900 --> 00:11:26,800
It's all right
if you don't.

145
00:11:40,900 --> 00:11:43,300
- Doc, you won't believe this.
- What is it?

146
00:11:43,500 --> 00:11:46,800
