153
00:12:16,800 --> 00:12:20,200
It's a true history.
No fiction, no lie.

154
00:12:20,400 --> 00:12:22,800
Africa,
two million years ago.

155
00:12:23,000 --> 00:12:26,300
Humans. Then they moved.

156
00:12:26,500 --> 00:12:28,400
Migrated.

157
00:12:28,600 --> 00:12:31,900
Ten thousand years ago,
civilization. You.

158
00:12:32,100 --> 00:12:34,000
This is me?

159
00:12:34,200 --> 00:12:36,100
Yeah, and me too. Us.

160
00:12:36,300 --> 00:12:39,800
Takers. Who are
the blue people?

161
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:43,600
