to give up... our dominion.

178
00:13:51,500 --> 00:13:53,300
We don't own the world.

179
00:13:53,500 --> 00:13:57,000
We're not kings here,
not gods.

180
00:13:57,300 --> 00:14:00,100
Can we give that up?

181
