will go outside.

201
00:15:17,900 --> 00:15:20,400
Then I will set his name aside,
and the next day I'll pick a new name.

202
00:15:20,600 --> 00:15:24,800
Everybody will have
their equal turn.

203
00:15:27,100 --> 00:15:30,500
And today
it's Lester Rodman.

204
00:15:33,700 --> 00:15:37,200
Where are you?
Lester Rodman.

205
00:15:37,400 --> 00:15:40,200
Lester Rodman?

