Come on.

213
00:16:03,500 --> 00:16:07,500
You got the ace, Pete?

214
00:16:07,800 --> 00:16:12,500
How about you, Ethan?
You got the ace?

215
00:16:12,500 --> 00:16:14,600
Come on, now.
Let me see that card.

216
00:16:14,900 --> 00:16:17,400
Don't be shy.
Let's see your card.

